<div class="post" id="piece_zero">
	<h1 onclick='show_default("piece_zero")' class="go_back_btn">
		<i class="fas fa-arrow-left" style="margin-right: 3px;"></i> Go Back 
	</h1>
	<h3 class="piece_header"> <%= @title1 %> </h3>
	<p>
Let us not kill each other <br>
with expectation <br>
nor drive each other mad <br>
with regret, <br>
let my unfulfilled dreams <br>
be my own to weep over, <br>
you pay your dues  <br>
to your feelings of neglect. <br>
 <br>
Let us throw to the winds <br>
these flowers of discontent, <br>
scatter to the breeze <br>
their withered petals, <br>
curled at the edges <br>
tired and weary they are <br>
bereft of the fragrance <br>
of sweet success. <br>
  <br>
Let us give away <br>
the boxes brimming <br>
with dark creatures <br>
before their wails clog our ears. <br>
Let them go and howl <br>
in the forgiving forest <br>
where the dry leaves <br>
will soak in their tears. <br>
 <br>
Instead, let us smile <br>
hold each other’s face, <br>
kiss both cheeks <br>
and enjoy the twilight. <br>
Let it draw colour <br>
from the drink <br>
in our goblets <br>
and expand its breath <br>
to fill the cool night. <br>
	</p>
	<div class="powered_by"> Powered by WordGates | The Home of Writers. </div>
</div>


<div class="post" id="piece_one">
	<h1 onclick='show_default("piece_one")' class="go_back_btn">
		<i class="fas fa-arrow-left" style="margin-right: 3px;"></i> Go Back 
	</h1>
	<h3 class="piece_header"> <%= @title2 %> </h3>
	<p>
I will not hold <br>
I will not tie <br>
My body or soul <br>
In silken ties. <br>
 <br>
I will not tie <br>
Myself in knots, <br>
In silken ties <br>
My freedoms rot. <br>
 <br>
Tied up in knots <br>
Your dreams to please, <br>
My freedoms rot <br>
As new pleasures tease. <br>
 <br>
My dreams to please <br>
I will breach and encroach, <br>
New pleasures tease <br>
I will hunt and poach. <br>
 <br>
Breached and broken, so encroached, <br>
Your tears can’t tie my body or soul. <br>
I will grab and I will poach, <br>
I will not be tied, I will not withhold <br>
	</p>
	<div class="powered_by"> Powered by WordGates | The Home of Writers. </div>
</div>


<div class="post" id="piece_two">
	<h1 onclick='show_default("piece_two")' class="go_back_btn">
		<i class="fas fa-arrow-left" style="margin-right: 3px;"></i> Go Back 
	</h1>
	<h3 class="piece_header"> <%= @title3 %> </h3>
	<p>
Act overnight  <br>
for me. <br>
Turn the tide. <br>
Throw out the rule book. <br>
Break the mould. <br>
Smash that cliché. <br>
Make me a gift <br>
of a brand new world, <br>
or an alarm clock <br>
that runs away. <br>
Even a sandwich toaster <br>
if it’s made from your heart, <br>
will do. <br>
	</p>
